            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Hd1e108">Rubrica 11</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De tranquillitate populi</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e114">
               
       De tranquillitate populorum. Rubrica. 11 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e119">
               
      <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Rd1e116">CAssiodorus eri li. i
      .c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e125">Omni
        quippe regno desiderabilis debet
        esse tranquillitas in qua et populi 
               proficiunt: et vtilitas gentium custoditur. Hec est
        enim bonarum artium mater: hec mortalium
        genus reparabili successione multiplicans 
               facultates protendit: mores extollit. Et 
               tantarum rerum ignarus agnoscitur qui eam 
               minime quesisse sentitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e146"> /
       <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Rd1e144">4. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e148">Cogi debet vt
        sit quietus qui suo vicio renuit esse 
               pacificus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e157"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Rd1e157">22 e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e159">Decet regalis apicis curam 
               generalitatis custodire concordiam. Ad laudem
        regnantis trahitur si ab omnibus pax ametur</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e167">
                /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Rd1e171">Libro. 2 e. 29.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e171">Regnantis est gloria 
               subiectorum ociosa tranquillitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e177"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Rd1e181">Lib. 3. e. 38</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e179">Principis opinionem longe lateque disseminat
        subiectorum custodita securitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e187"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Rd1e192">Li. 5. e. 39</ref>
        <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e189">Quies suauissima populi et dispositio 
               tranquilla regionum preconium probatur esse 
               regnantium.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e199"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Rd1e205">Lib. 11. e. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e201">Furoris genus est in 
               seculo pacato turbulento studere proposito. <!--118.xml-->
               </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
